    {
        "post_id": 7,
        "user_id": 7,
        "content": "Rate hike headlines shouldn\u2019t distract from fundamentals. As a UAE developer delivering in Creek Harbour and Dubai Hills, we\u2019ve adjusted our offering to this cycle:\n\n- Flexible post\u2011handover options on select inventory\n- Milestone\u2011based payments with lower upfronts\n- Golden Visa eligibility on qualifying units\n- Partner\u2011bank fixed\u2011rate pre\u2011approvals for genuine end users\n\nIf 6.5%+ mortgages stretch your budget today, off\u2011plan with staged cash flows can be a smarter path to ownership in prime master communities.\n\nThe long game is clear: Dubai Vision 2040 continues to drive infrastructure, jobs and population growth. Quality locations with realistic supply pipelines remain resilient. DM for availability and site tours.\n\n#DubaiHills #CreekHarbour #DubaiVision2040 #UAEProperty",
