        "content": "User 8 reposted a post from User 0. Repost content: \ud83d\udea8 BREAKING \u2014 Dubai Real Estate Market Update:\nUAE Central Bank raises benchmark interest rate by 50 basis points, pushing average mortgage rates above 6.5%. RERA warns of potential affordability pressure on first-time buyers in mid-market segments.\n\n#DubaiRealEstate #UAEProperty #PropertyMarket. ",
        "created_at": "2026-04-27 08:09:20.257740",
