                "user_id": 9,
                "content": "50 bps hike pushes more people to rent, not buy. In Marina and JVC we\u2019re already near full occupancy and renewals are firm. This isn\u2019t a crash\u2014just tighter affordability for financed buyers. Cash is still active and yields look better. As landlords we\u2019ll price renewals per the RERA calculator and keep units well-maintained. If you\u2019re renting, consider locking a longer term for stability; if you\u2019re buying with a mortgage, stress test at 7\u20138%. Long-term holders will ride this out.",
